remarks:
Theorem *3.2 of [WhiteheadRussell] p. 111, expressed with primitive connectives.  (Contributed by NM, 29-Dec-1992.)  (Proof shortened by Josh Purinton, 29-Dec-2000.) 

---

 In classical logic, this is just a restatement of ~ pm3.2 .  In intuitionistic logic, it still holds, but is weaker than pm3.2. (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 12-May-2015.)
